verbose_text: Measuring the hepatic and adrenal Sod2 expression by quantitative real-time polymerase chain reaction (qPCR) we determined, as expected, that Sod2 expression was about twofold diminished in Aaas KO/Sod2 Het mice under a control or paraquat diet compared to wild-type (WT) and Aaas KO mice of the same diet (XREF_FIG A).
